23
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:52,020
[Episode 19]

24
00:01:58,100 --> 00:01:58,900
The Haoque Sword.

25
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:04,940
Will I be able to see

26
00:02:04,980 --> 00:02:06,420
the Xiao Family's
imperial sword technique,

27
00:02:06,420 --> 00:02:07,060
the Lieguo Sword Technique?

28
00:02:07,860 --> 00:02:08,900
I'm afraid not.

29
00:02:09,580 --> 00:02:10,420
He's not good

30
00:02:10,420 --> 00:02:11,380
at the Lieguo Sword Technique.

31
00:02:11,700 --> 00:02:13,020
I do know a sword technique

32
00:02:13,020 --> 00:02:14,020
called the second-best sword technique,

33
00:02:14,860 --> 00:02:16,300
and its my own creation.

34
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:18,980
Back then, I was thinking

35
00:02:18,980 --> 00:02:19,900
that if I claimed to be second best,

36
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:21,540
no one would claim to be the best.

37
00:02:21,780 --> 00:02:23,020
But, he still couldn't

38
00:02:23,020 --> 00:02:23,900
master that as well.

39
00:02:24,620 --> 00:02:25,300
So he went back home

40
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:26,540
and created another sword technique,

41
00:02:26,660 --> 00:02:27,620
the third-best sword technique.

42
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:29,460
That's right.

43
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:31,460
The third-best sword technique.

44
00:02:32,060 --> 00:02:33,460
Out of all the best sword techniques,

45
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:36,060
Mine is second only to Mr. Li's,

46
00:02:36,540 --> 00:02:39,620
so my sword technique is called
the third-best sword technique.

47
00:02:40,580 --> 00:02:41,820
You call it
the third-best sword technique?

48
00:02:42,460 --> 00:02:43,260
Nice.

49
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:44,540
I call my fighting style

50
00:02:44,780 --> 00:02:46,060
"Beat Them All Up".

51
00:03:06,180 --> 00:03:07,700
He only has the eighth-best sword.

52
00:03:08,340 --> 00:03:09,900
How can he compare to the Wuji Pole?

53
00:03:34,780 --> 00:03:35,660
Baili Dongjun!

54
00:03:35,980 --> 00:03:37,300
Ruofeng, I'm here!

55
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:44,820
You...

56
00:03:45,700 --> 00:03:46,420
Why did you come here?

57
00:03:46,540 --> 00:03:46,940
Ruofeng,

58
00:03:47,420 --> 00:03:48,500
you called my name loudly just now

59
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:49,060
to ask me

60
00:03:49,060 --> 00:03:49,980
to help you, right?

61
00:03:50,900 --> 00:03:51,580
I called you

62
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:53,380
to escape with Master!

63
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:56,900
None of you shall leave!

64
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:01,260
Stop fighting!

65
00:04:26,900 --> 00:04:28,540
If you're under the age of 30,

66
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:29,780
you might call yourself invincible.

67
00:04:30,220 --> 00:04:31,620
If you're over the age of 30,

68
00:04:31,700 --> 00:04:33,260
less than ten people might defeat you

69
00:04:33,500 --> 00:04:35,580
and only three people at most
can kill you.

70
00:04:36,140 --> 00:04:37,700
I'm one of the three people.

71
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:39,380
But I won't kill you.

72
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:41,540
I will give you the answer you seek,

73
00:04:42,020 --> 00:04:43,180
but after this,

74
00:04:43,260 --> 00:04:44,900
whatever my disciple,

75
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:47,100
Prince Langya of Tianqi City,

76
00:04:48,060 --> 00:04:49,420
wants to do in the future,

77
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:50,500
you have to help him.

78
00:04:54,340 --> 00:04:57,460
Water from the great river
comes from Heaven!

79
00:05:29,900 --> 00:05:31,180
You want to know the answer?

80
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:33,780
Sure, I shall tell you the answer.

81
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:36,460
I am the one who has dominated the world

82
00:05:36,580 --> 00:05:37,580
for 30 years

83
00:05:37,620 --> 00:05:39,220
under the Academy.

84
00:05:39,300 --> 00:05:40,140
60 years ago,

85
00:05:40,180 --> 00:05:41,180
I was the one who wielded
the Ablaze and Cold Swords

86
00:05:41,300 --> 00:05:43,780
and defeated Wei Changshu
from the Famous Swords Manor,

87
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:45,980
after which I was known
as the Kunlun Sword Deity.

88
00:05:46,020 --> 00:05:46,980
90 years ago,

89
00:05:46,990 --> 00:05:48,990
clad in tattered clothes
and armed with a broken sword,

90
00:05:49,020 --> 00:05:51,300
I was the one who exterminated
the Demonic Sect.

91
00:05:51,380 --> 00:05:52,740
120 years ago,

92
00:05:52,740 --> 00:05:54,780
I was the one who drank, lived,

93
00:05:54,780 --> 00:05:56,740
and created the Poetry-Sword Technique

94
00:05:57,380 --> 00:05:58,340
with the Poetry Deity.

95
00:05:58,740 --> 00:06:00,500
And, to answer your question
you want to know the most,

96
00:06:00,580 --> 00:06:01,940
150 years ago,

97
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:03,980
I was the one

98
00:06:04,020 --> 00:06:05,940
who founded

99
00:06:06,420 --> 00:06:08,220
Baixiao Hall on my own.

100
00:06:08,580 --> 00:06:09,820
A divine touched on my head,

101
00:06:09,980 --> 00:06:11,580
and thus I was given an eternal life.

102
00:06:11,940 --> 00:06:14,020
I am now over 180 years old.

103
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:15,540
I am your elder.

104
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:17,460
How dare you fight your elder?

105
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:19,180
Preposterous.

106
00:06:20,780 --> 00:06:21,300
So...

107
00:06:23,300 --> 00:06:24,820
It really exists after all.

108
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:27,260
You've already guessed most of it,

109
00:06:27,300 --> 00:06:28,940
so why do you seek this answer?

110
00:06:41,220 --> 00:06:41,980
I didn't expect

111
00:06:42,820 --> 00:06:43,540
that immortality

112
00:06:43,540 --> 00:06:44,500
would exist in this world.

113
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:00,220
There's no such thing

114
00:07:00,260 --> 00:07:02,020
as immortality in this world.

115
00:07:03,300 --> 00:07:04,420
Anything in this world

116
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:06,260
is bound to return somewhere.

117
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:08,940
It's just that I've been trapped
in the mortal world...

118
00:07:12,620 --> 00:07:13,540
for too long.

119
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:09,740
Ruofeng.

120
00:08:10,620 --> 00:08:11,780
Are my eyes fooling me?

121
00:08:12,940 --> 00:08:13,500
Is...

122
00:08:14,100 --> 00:08:15,060
Is that our master?

123
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:17,380
Why does he look

124
00:08:17,380 --> 00:08:18,420
as young as I am now?

125
00:08:19,380 --> 00:08:20,260
Our master

126
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:22,700
is just like his name.

127
00:08:23,580 --> 00:08:24,420
Changsheng,
[*Lit: immortal]

128
00:08:25,260 --> 00:08:25,980
an immortal.

129
00:08:45,180 --> 00:08:46,260
You've already found

130
00:08:46,300 --> 00:08:47,220
the answer you seek.

131
00:08:47,940 --> 00:08:49,540
Don't forget

132
00:08:50,380 --> 00:08:51,300
my little favor.

133
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:52,380
But, Baixiao Hall

134
00:08:52,380 --> 00:08:53,660
never interferes
in the court's affairs.

135
00:08:54,580 --> 00:08:54,980
That's the rule

136
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:56,180
set by our founder, right?

137
00:08:57,700 --> 00:08:59,020
I'm asking you to help him,

138
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:01,140
not Baixiao Hall.

139
00:09:01,260 --> 00:09:01,940
Besides,

140
00:09:02,300 --> 00:09:03,980
I am the founder.

141
00:09:08,780 --> 00:09:09,700
You have seen

142
00:09:10,620 --> 00:09:11,580
what you wanted to see.

143
00:09:13,340 --> 00:09:14,860
Write it down in Baixiao Hall's records,

144
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:17,180
but don't let anyone else know.

145
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:18,260
Understand?

146
00:09:19,580 --> 00:09:20,060
I...

147
00:09:21,620 --> 00:09:22,220
No.

148
00:09:22,900 --> 00:09:23,380
Elder.

149
00:09:26,100 --> 00:09:26,940
I understand.

150
00:09:28,780 --> 00:09:30,900
Since we look about the same age now,

151
00:09:31,180 --> 00:09:32,980
you don't have to call me Elder.

152
00:09:33,180 --> 00:09:34,620
It makes me sound old.

153
00:09:36,860 --> 00:09:37,260
You may leave now.

154
00:09:41,780 --> 00:09:42,700
I'll take my leave, then.

155
00:09:43,020 --> 00:09:44,460
If you ever return to Tianqi,

156
00:09:45,180 --> 00:09:46,460
do visit Baixiao Hall.

157
00:09:56,820 --> 00:09:57,620
Xiao Ruofeng.

158
00:09:59,100 --> 00:09:59,820
Yes, Master.

159
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:04,940
Master.

160
00:10:05,740 --> 00:10:07,980
So your real name is Ji Changsheng?
[*Ji and chicken have the same sound]

161
00:10:08,980 --> 00:10:10,220
What kind of name is that?

162
00:10:10,300 --> 00:10:11,020
You might as well call me

163
00:10:11,020 --> 00:10:12,100
Gou Changsheng.
[*Gou means dog]

164
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:17,580
When I was young,

165
00:10:17,980 --> 00:10:19,580
I didn't expect to become immortal.

166
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:23,180
My real name is Ji Huxie.

167
00:10:24,820 --> 00:10:26,180
My successor you saw earlier

168
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,820
is as strong as I was back then.

169
00:10:28,300 --> 00:10:29,460
With his help,

170
00:10:29,940 --> 00:10:30,820
you have a better chance

171
00:10:31,300 --> 00:10:32,700
of securing the throne.

172
00:10:35,580 --> 00:10:36,500
That young man back in Tianqi

173
00:10:36,580 --> 00:10:38,300
who fights with a spear

174
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:39,460
is pretty impressive too.

175
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:42,060
As for the one standing behind there,

176
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:43,980
forget about him.

177
00:10:45,060 --> 00:10:46,460
He's too special.

178
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:48,700
I understand.

179
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:56,300
Alright, you may also leave now.

180
00:10:56,980 --> 00:10:57,980
There's somewhere I need to go.

181
00:10:58,220 --> 00:10:59,860
I'll write you a letter.

182
00:11:00,340 --> 00:11:01,300
If you want to,

183
00:11:01,980 --> 00:11:03,220
you can join us.

184
00:11:03,980 --> 00:11:06,220
Who knows, we can have

185
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:08,460
a round of drinks.

186
00:11:12,340 --> 00:11:12,980
Master.

187
00:11:14,460 --> 00:11:15,460
Was there any truth

188
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:18,500
in what you said earlier?

189
00:11:20,100 --> 00:11:21,100
Why do I feel

190
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:22,700
that this might be

191
00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:25,420
the last time I see you?

192
00:11:26,060 --> 00:11:27,460
Are you an idiot?

193
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:32,300
When have I ever deceived you?

194
00:11:32,460 --> 00:11:34,180
You just don't trust me.

195
00:11:34,980 --> 00:11:35,620
I told you

196
00:11:35,620 --> 00:11:36,980
that I drank with the Poetry Deity,

197
00:11:37,060 --> 00:11:37,620
and you

198
00:11:37,620 --> 00:11:38,860
turned your backs and rolled your eyes.

199
00:11:39,220 --> 00:11:40,220
You think I didn't notice?

200
00:11:42,740 --> 00:11:43,220
Okay.

201
00:11:44,460 --> 00:11:45,580
I hope that this time,

202
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:47,460
you're not bluffing us.

203
00:11:49,980 --> 00:11:50,820
Farewell.

204
00:12:04,220 --> 00:12:05,300
Baili Dongjun.

205
00:12:07,620 --> 00:12:08,220
Master.

206
00:12:20,460 --> 00:12:21,340
Master, don't move.

207
00:12:21,700 --> 00:12:22,820
You don't move.

208
00:12:28,660 --> 00:12:29,780
Help me back to the carriage.

209
00:12:30,380 --> 00:12:30,940
Yes, Master.

210
00:12:34,420 --> 00:12:35,060
Carry me on your back.

211
00:12:46,620 --> 00:12:47,380
Martial Uncle Baili,

212
00:12:48,780 --> 00:12:50,380
why has Mr. Li turned young?

213
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:52,100
Let's get back to the carriage first.

214
00:12:59,090 --> 00:13:00,020
What happened to him?

215
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:04,740
Ji Ruofeng was right.

216
00:13:05,820 --> 00:13:06,860
I am losing

217
00:13:06,860 --> 00:13:08,340
all my internal strength.

218
00:13:08,980 --> 00:13:11,700
Too bad he came late

219
00:13:12,340 --> 00:13:12,980
and couldn't witness

220
00:13:13,020 --> 00:13:15,420
such a magnificent sight.

221
00:13:18,700 --> 00:13:20,980
Now, even you can easily

222
00:13:21,780 --> 00:13:23,300
kill me,

223
00:13:24,100 --> 00:13:26,500
the best martial artist in the world.

224
00:13:27,300 --> 00:13:28,820
What exactly is going on?

225
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:30,900
What's going on?

226
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:32,980
You'll know someday.

227
00:13:34,700 --> 00:13:36,260
Don't worry about me.

228
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:38,860
I'm just feeling a little weak.

229
00:13:39,340 --> 00:13:40,260
I'm not dying.

230
00:13:40,500 --> 00:13:41,300
Now,

231
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:44,700
I just want to get some sleep.

232
00:13:50,580 --> 00:13:51,260
Master,

233
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:52,300
don't sleep.

234
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:53,740
You'd never wake up, then.

235
00:14:01,940 --> 00:14:03,020
Right now, all I want

236
00:14:03,060 --> 00:14:04,460
is to get a good sleep.

237
00:14:04,460 --> 00:14:06,020
Master, believe me.

238
00:14:06,140 --> 00:14:07,020
You can't fall asleep.

239
00:14:07,140 --> 00:14:08,380
Believe me.

240
00:14:09,540 --> 00:14:11,180
This is not the first time.

241
00:14:14,780 --> 00:14:17,060
Just head westward

242
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:19,180
and I'll be awake in the morning.

243
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:22,660
Please do me this favor.

244
00:14:25,300 --> 00:14:25,900
Master.

245
00:14:30,300 --> 00:14:30,780
Master.

246
00:14:31,420 --> 00:14:32,940
[Nanjue]

247
00:14:32,940 --> 00:14:33,860
Have you heard?

248
00:14:34,260 --> 00:14:35,780
The Rain Demon and his disciple

249
00:14:35,860 --> 00:14:36,860
have been traveling
around almost half of Nanjue.

250
00:14:37,860 --> 00:14:38,580
That demon

251
00:14:38,580 --> 00:14:40,220
seems to be heading

252
00:14:40,380 --> 00:14:41,420
to Dongyue Lake

253
00:14:41,740 --> 00:14:42,980
to challenge some sword deity.

254
00:14:43,420 --> 00:14:44,940
I heard lots of martial arts masters

255
00:14:44,940 --> 00:14:45,540
have been there.

256
00:14:45,860 --> 00:14:47,900
Back then the Poetry Deity could kill
one man within every ten steps he took

257
00:14:47,940 --> 00:14:49,060
with no trace to be found
for a thousand li.

258
00:14:49,460 --> 00:14:50,420
Now, the Rain Demon

259
00:14:50,540 --> 00:14:51,620
keeps his sword sheathed,

260
00:14:51,700 --> 00:14:52,660
traveling far just to fight.

261
00:14:52,860 --> 00:14:53,580
I wonder

262
00:14:53,620 --> 00:14:54,820
if he'll become a future legend.

263
00:14:55,460 --> 00:14:57,620
How literary of you.

264
00:14:59,220 --> 00:15:00,700
But, I did hear

265
00:15:01,140 --> 00:15:02,540
that the Rain Demon

266
00:15:02,900 --> 00:15:04,420
has been countering attacks
throughout his journey,

267
00:15:04,900 --> 00:15:06,700
but has never killed
any of his assailants.

268
00:15:06,740 --> 00:15:07,740
Only fighting, and not killing?

269
00:15:08,700 --> 00:15:10,180
Has that demon truly changed?

270
00:15:12,700 --> 00:15:13,220
Come on.

271
00:15:13,220 --> 00:15:14,020
Master, you hear that?

272
00:15:14,620 --> 00:15:15,140
You're stirring

273
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:16,340
quite a lot of commotion.

274
00:15:16,860 --> 00:15:18,820
All that's left is to put a flag on you

275
00:15:18,940 --> 00:15:21,300
that says, "The Rain Demon is here".

276
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:23,380
But, Master,

277
00:15:24,340 --> 00:15:25,460
if this keeps up,

278
00:15:25,900 --> 00:15:27,340
are you sure we won't die of exhaustion

279
00:15:27,660 --> 00:15:28,380
before we reach Dongyue Lake?

280
00:15:29,300 --> 00:15:31,020
Before you kill someone,
you need to sharpen your sword.

281
00:15:48,140 --> 00:15:48,620
What is it?

282
00:15:50,940 --> 00:15:52,180
It's that old geezer, Chen.

283
00:15:53,620 --> 00:15:55,300
It's the Rain Demon.

284
00:15:56,060 --> 00:15:58,140
