00:25:17,460 --> 00:25:19,140
Actually, it wasn't a big deal.

423
00:25:19,380 --> 00:25:20,780
When I was young,

424
00:25:20,900 --> 00:25:22,980
I went to Huanglong Mountain

425
00:25:23,100 --> 00:25:24,140
