444
00:26:01,660 --> 00:26:03,220
There are too many eyes
and too much gossip

445
00:26:03,220 --> 00:26:04,180
in Tianqi,

446
00:26:05,100 --> 00:26:06,180
so I had to leave.

447
00:26:06,540 --> 00:26:07,500
That's why I...

448
00:26:07,500 --> 00:26:08,580
That's why you got me

